1. Always focus on menu based bash scripts.
2. This will be a category based repo with multiple tools inside each category.
3. Tools should be categoried and structured in a way that is easier to find and interact.
4. If you are not sure about on which category to include the tools on, always ask me instead of assuming.
5. Make a entry file on the root which lists the cateogry of commands and under each category keep the similar list of menu with tools.
6. 0 on each menu should bring flow to before menu.
7. Under each category, keep each tools as a seperate file that are easier to manage and maintain.
